    What is an escort to a patient?
    A patient escort works one-on-one with a patient to manage their immediate needs while freeing medical staff to treat others in their care. Your duties include the transport of a patient from one unit or location to another. You may also transfer individuals from a wheelchair to a bed and vice versa.
